ts client it invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe the firm also invests in the alternative investments markets in hedge funds real estate and private equity through ann external manager for its equity investments the firm primarily invests in value and growth stocks of allcap companies including largecap midcap and smallcap companies for its fixed income investments it typically invests cash and shortterm securities taxable bonds municipal bonds and investmentgrade securities the firm employs a combination of fundamental quantitative and qualitative analysis with a bottomup investment approach it employs a mix of inhouse and external research to make its investment decisions the firm operates as a subsidiary of bessemer trust company na bessemer investment management was founded in  and is based in new york new york with additional offices in atlanta georgia boston massachusetts chicago illinois dallas texas grand cayman cayman islands london united kingdom los angeles california miami florida naples florida palm beach florida san francisco california washington district of columbia wilmington delaware and woodbridge new jersey detailed description  fifth avenuenew york ny united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwbessemercom key executives for bessemer investment management llc mr john allen hilton jr chief executive officer and director mr marc david stern senior managing director and president mr thaddeus r shelly iii senior managing director midatlantic and south and southeast region head mr robert c elliott esq senior managing director and head of northeast central west and international region mr john gerard macdonald cpa managing director chief financial officer treasurer and member of the board of directors compensation as of fiscal year  similar private companies by industry company name region visory llc united states  road partners llc united states t partners llc united states jumpcom inc united states  ontario inc united 